  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="/facilitators-collective"><h3>Seeds for Justice Facilitators Collective</h3></a></span>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-node-image">        <div class="field-content view-mode-full"></div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p style="text-align: justify;"><img height="239" width="303" style="font-size: 13.008px; width: 325px; height: 256px; float: right; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px;" class="media-element file-default" typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://kwic.info/sites/default/files/FINAL%20B%26W%20Facilitators%20Collective%20Logo%20%28REDESIGN-May%2012%2C%202015%29%20copy.gif" alt="" />The Facilitators Collective is a Seeds for Justice initiative hosted under the Kawartha World Issues Centre. Entirely <strong>youth</strong>-driven, the Collective’s goal is to develop and deliver <strong>social </strong>and <strong>environmental </strong>justice-themed workshops to youth in Peterborough and the surrounding areas.</p></div>  </div>  
