  <div class="views-field views-field-title">        <span class="field-content"><a href="/alti-library"><h3>alti library</h3></a></span>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-node-image">        <div class="field-content view-mode-full"></div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p><strong>Alti Library</strong><br /><br />
	KWIC’s Resource Centre is located in the Environmental Sciences Building, B101, and contains a wide variety of books and magazines, including children’s books and teacher resource materials on social justice and environmental issues. The centre is open from 7:00am - 7:00pm and books are checked out using the self-checkout form. Books can be returned in the book box located inside. </p>
<p class="MsoNormal">An on-line directory of materials can be searched on-line at <a href="http://www.prcsa.ca/library"><span style="color: #0000ff;">www.prcsa.ca/library</span></a></p></div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-upload">        <div class="field-content"></div>  </div>  
